cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM

This paper deals with image enhancement and recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories. The use of Convolution Neural Network (CNN) for learning the mapping between low and high resolution images is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of Tamil images, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) category.
